---
name: undrift
description: >
  Analyses the last 50 sessions of the current project to detect recurring
  corrections, repeated instructions, and reverted changes. Generates a
  CLAUDE.md.proposed file with distilled rules to prevent Claude from drifting
  back into bad habits. Invoke when the user asks to review past sessions,
  extract correction patterns, improve CLAUDE.md rules, or says things like
  "you keep doing X wrong", "mine my sessions", "what am I always correcting",
  "undrift my sessions" or "undrift".
agents: [main_agent]
